<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#4c084a6e6dbc655a6697e16fc65a9497>.
<#4c084a6e6dbc655a6697e16fc65a9497> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/79c2ad4f-a216-4636-9714-713adc3c3a6a>;
