<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9f6f7850-fb42-4910-a4d6-15d8004e15df> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/klimatolog_smhi.se>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-download-grid-archive.smhi.se/feed/9>, <https://opendata-view.smhi.se/grid-archive/mesanG_extent/wms?service=wms&request=getcapabilities>, <https://opendata.smhi.se/gridarchive/index_met>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/temperatur-och-vind/temperatur/historisk-data-i-grib-format/sa-fungerar-grib-format>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/temperatur-och-vind/temperatur/historisk-data-i-grib-format/mesan-g>;
