<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/cb15b040-32bf-11ea-91f2-0b81cad13edd> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Snö"@sv, "Öppna data"@sv, "Meteorologi"@sv, "Observation"@sv, "HVD"@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/CONT>;
