<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#7fd0e47ac4cba31d6b82d848e9590625>.
<#7fd0e47ac4cba31d6b82d848e9590625> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9e3c0b20-cdb2-11eb-9269-d991226864d8>;
