<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/be9d3f7b-2fbc-4dca-92f9-baee027a3f89> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/kundtjanst_smhi.se>;
