    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2001-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/616> <http://entryscape.org/terms/metadataIdentifier> "630a62fb-10a9-4d44-9004-29a3d3717d3c";
