}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#5b21dae2fe34842ca02935d7d7e057d1>.
<#5b21dae2fe34842ca02935d7d7e057d1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U21357>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-05-15T07:07:20.317Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
