_:b0__37896 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Källa: Nationella emissionsdatabasen\\n"@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N85515> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-06-09"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Utsläpp till luft av ammoniak (NH3), arbetsmaskiner, kg"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/GOVE>;
