_:b0__38328 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "1992-09-27"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "1991-04-17"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/zgf1-z384> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__44356.
_:b0__44356 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2013-06"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
