<#9377d40bc4a04487613e81a1a1a72603> {
<https://doi.org/10.5878/001789> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__69774.
_:b0__69774 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/author>;
